{"title":"VSCode安装使用编程字体FiraCode","uid":"ca5f7333fd4afa33ba15d97463d47073","slug":"VSCode安装使用编程字体FiraCode","date":"2019-04-24T02:21:10.000Z","updated":"2021-12-05T14:34:08.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/VSCode安装使用编程字体FiraCode.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>FiraCode字体是一个可以把编程中常用的组合符号优化显示的字体<br><img src=\"../images/VSCode%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93FiraCode/image-20200408143909604.png\" alt=\"效果.png\"></p>\n<p>下面开始在VSCode中的配置</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>首先在<a href=\"https://github.com/tonsky/FiraCode\">FiraCode</a>的github页面下载字体<br><img src=\"../images/VSCode%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93FiraCode/image-20200408143820477.png\" alt=\"下载.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>把下载的压缩包解压，然后找到ttf文件夹，全部选中，右键安装即可</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在VSCode中的配置</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-js\" data-language=\"js\"><code class=\"language-js\">&quot;editor.fontFamily&quot;: &quot;&#39;Fira Code&#39;, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace&quot;,&#x2F;&#x2F;添加上FiraCode字体\n&quot;editor.fontLigatures&quot;: true,&#x2F;&#x2F;开启连体字</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\